
# Title
Simulation of an epoxy monomer

# Intialization
units          real
dimension      3d
boundary       p p p
atom_style     atomic

# Atom Definition
read_data      epoxy.lmpdat
replicate      1 1 1

# Settings
velocity       all create 298.15 4928459 rot yes mom yes dist gaussian
fix            ensemble all nvt temp 298.15 298.15 100 tchain 1

timestep       2.0

# Output
thermo_style   one
thermo         50

# Run the simulation
run            50
